answers.hobbies: I spend my weekends hiking in the mountains and experimenting with watercolor painting. I also love teaching kids at the local community center about sustainable living.
answers.study_work: The ability to solve complex environmental challenges while working with diverse communities. Every day brings new puzzles that require both technical expertise and human empathy.
answers.mistake: I once pushed for a project without properly listening to the community's needs. It taught me that the best solutions come from collaboration, not just expertise.
answers.beyond_title: A perpetual learner who believes small actions create ripples of change
